HEADWORD: Vaulting
<hw>Vault"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
constructing vaults; a vaulted construction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Act of one who vaults or leaps.</def>⟦br⟧
